or**\n\nIf no body is parsed, ctx.request.body should remain undefined so that downstream middleware (including koa-bodyparser) can handle it appropriately.\n\n**Steps to Reproduce**\n\nUse koa-body in a Koa app.\nSend a request without a body (e.g., a GET request or an empty POST request).\nObserve that ctx.request.body is {} instead of undefined, which may prevent other middleware from handling the request properly.\n\n**Possible Fix**\n\nAvoid setting  \"{}\" when the request body is not parsed.","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/koajs/koa-body/issues/238/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/koajs/koa-body/issues/238/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed","pinned_comment":null,"score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/koajs/router/issues/46","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/koajs/router","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/koajs/router/issues/46/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/koajs/router/issues/46/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/koajs/router/issues/46/events","html_url":"https://github.com/koajs/router/issues/46","id":549194314,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU1NDkxOTQzMTQ=","number":46,"title":"Router runs middleware on routes, which are not in array.","user":{"login":"pantuchy","id":10475599,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEwNDc1NTk5","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/10475599?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/pantuchy","html_url":"https://github.com/pantuchy","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pantuchy/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pantuchy/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pantuchy/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pantuchy/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pantuchy/su